\c 33
\s Basa renharirire
\p
\v 1 Zvino shoko raJehovha rakasvika kwandiri richiti:
\v 2 Mwanakomana wemunhu, taura kuvana vevanhu vako, uti kwavari: Pandinouisa munondo pamusoro penyika, kana vanhu venyika iyo vakatora munhu pamiganhu yavo vakamuita nharirire yavo,
\v 3 paanoona munondo uchiuya pamusoro penyika, akaridza hwamanda ndokuyambira vanhu;
\v 4 zvino ani nani anonzwa kurira kwehwamanda akasayambirika, kana munondo ukauya ukamubvisa, , ropa rake richava pamusoro pemusoro wake.
\v 5 wakanzwa kurira kwehwamanda, akasayambirika, ropa rake richava pamusoro pake, asi anoyambirika achaponesa mweya wake.
\v 6 Asi kana nharirire ichiona munondo uchiuya ikasaridza hwamanda, vanhu vanhu ndokusayambira, kana munondo ukauya ukabvisa munhu pakati pavo, wabviswa nechivi chake asi ropa rake richatsvakwa muruoko rwenharirire.
\p
\v 7 Saizvozvowo iwe mwanakomana wemunhu, ndakakuisa kuva nharirire kuimba yaIsraeri; naizvozvo uchanzwa shoko pamuromo wangu ugovanyeverera ini.
\v 8 Kana ndichiti kune wakaipa: Iwe wakaipa, uchafa zvirokwazvo, kana iwe ukasataura kuti uyambire wakaipa kubva panzira yake, wakaipa uyo achafira muchivi chake, asi ropa rake ndicharitsvaka paruoko rwako.
\v 9 Asi kana iwe ukayambira wakaipa panzira yake kuti abve pairi, kana akasatendeuka panzira yake, iye achaira muchivi chake, asi iwe wanunura mweya wako.
\p
\v 10 Naizvozvo iwe, mwanakomana wemunhu, iti kuimba yaIsraeri: Imwi munotaura seizvi muchiti: Nokuti zvitadzo zvedu nezvivi zvedu zviri pamusoro pedu, uye tionopera mazviri; zvino tichararama sei?
\v 11 Uti kwavari: Neupenyu hwangu, anoreva Ishe Jehovha handifariri rufu rwewakaipa, asi kuti wakaipa atendeuke panzira yake ararame. Tendeukai, tendeukai panzira dzenyu dzakaipa, nokuti muchafirei, imwi imba yaIsraeri?
\p
\v 12 Zvino iwe, mwanakomana wemunhu, uti kuvana vevanhu vako: Kururama kwewakarurama hakungamununuri pazuva rekudarika kwake; uye kana kuri kuipa kwewakaipa haangawi nako pazuva raakatendeuka kubva pauipi hwake, uye wakarurama haangararami ne\add kururama kwake\add* nezuva raanotadza.
\v 13 Pandichati kune wakarurama uchararama zvirokwazvo, kana iye achivimba nekururama kwake, ndokuita chitadzo, kururama kwake kwese hakungarangarirwi;, asi nekuti kweuipi hwake hwaaita, achahufira.
\v 14 Uye kana ndichiti kune wakaipa: Uchafa zvekufa; kana akatendeuka kubva pachivi chake, ndokuita mitongo nekururama;
\v 15 wakaipa akadzosa rubatso, akaripa zvakapambwa, akafamba muzvimiso zveupenyu, kuti asaita chitadzo, achararama zvirokwazvo, haangafi.
\v 16 Hakuna chimwe chezvivi zvake zvaakaita chicharangarirwa kwaari; waita mutongo nekururama achararama zvirokwazvo.
\p
\v 17 Asi vana vevanhu vako vanoti: Nzira yaIshe haina kururama; asi kana vari ivo, nzira yavo ndiyo isina kururama.
\v 18 Kana akarurama akatendeuka kubva pakururama kwake ndokuita chitadzo, achafawo nekuda kwacho.
\v 19 Asi kana wakaipa katendeuka kubva pauipi hwake, ndokuita mutongo nekururama, iye achararama naizvozvo.
\p
\v 20 Zvakadaro munoti: Nzira yaIshe haina kururama. haiwa imba yaIsraeri, ndichakutongai umwe neumwe zvichitevera nzira yake.
\s Kuwa kweJerusarema
\p
\v 21 Zvino negore regumi namaviri rokutapwa kwedu, nomwedzi wegumi, nezuva reshanu romwedzi, umwe akange apukunyuka muJerusarema akasvika kwandiri, achiti: Guta rakundwa.
\v 22 Zvino ruoko rwaJehovha rwakange ruri pamusoro pangu madekwani, iye akapukunyuka asati asvika; akange ashamisa muromo wangu, kusvikira iye achisvika kwandiri mangwanani; muromo wangu ukashamiswa, ndikasazova mbeveve.
\p
\v 23 Shoko raJehovha rikasvika kwandiri, richiti,
\v 24 Mwanakomana womunhu, vanhu vagere panzvimbo idzo dzakaparadzwa munyika yaIsraeri, vanotaura vachiti: Abhurahama akange ari mumwechete, akagara nhaka yenyika; asi isu tiri vazhinji, nyika yapiwesu ive nhaka yedu.
\v 25 Naizvozvo chiti kwavari: Zvanzi naIshe Jehovha: Munodya nyama pamwe chete neropa, muchitarira zvifananidzo zvenyu nameso enyu nokuteura ropa; zvino mungapiwa nyika sei?
\v 26 Munovimba nomunondo wenyu, munoita zvinonyangadza, munochinya umwe neumwe wenyu mukadzi wowokwake; zvino mungapiwa nyika sei?
\v 27 Chiti kwavari: Zvanzi naIshe Jehovha: Noupenyu hwangu, zvirokwazvo vari panzvimbo dzakaparadzwa vachaparadzwa nomunondo, ari kubani ndichamuisa kuzvikara kuti adyiwe nazvo; vari munhare nomumapako vachafa nehosha yakaipa.
\v 28 Nyika ndichaiita dongo nechishamiso, kuzvikudza kwayo pamusoro pesimba rayo kuchapera, namakomo aVaIsraeri achaitwa matongo, kuti kurege kuzova nomunhu unopfuura napo.
\v 29 Zvino vachaziva kuti ndini Jehovha, kana ndaita nyika dongo nechishamiso, nokuda kwezvinonyangadza zvavo zvese zvavakaita.
\p
\v 30 Asi kana uriwe, mwanakomana womunhu, vana vavanhu vako vanokureva vari pamasvingo avo nomumikova yedzimba dzavo, vanotaurirana umwe neumwe achiti kuhama yake: Douya hako, unzwe shoko rinobva kuna Jehovha.
\v 31 Vanouya kwauri sezvinoita vanhu, vanogara pamberi pako sezvinoita vanhu vangu, vanonzwa mashoko ako, asi havaaiti; nokuti vanotaura zvorudo nemiromo yavo, asi moyo yavo inotevera fuma yavo.
\v 32 Zvino tarira, iwe wakaita kwavari somunhu anovaimbira sorwiyo rworudo runoimbwa nounenzwi rinofadza, unogona kuridza mbira kwazvo, nokuti vanonzwa mashoko ako, asi havaaiti.
\v 33 Zvino kana izvi zvichiitwa nokuti zvirokwazvo hazvimboregi kuitika, nenguva iyo vachaziva kuti muporofita akange ari pakati pavo.